-- Risanamento Agrees to Sell Falck Property Outside Milan for $563 Million
-- B y   M a r c o   B e r t a c c h e
-- 2010-10-22T15:19:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/risanamento-agrees-to-sell-falck-property-outside-milan-for-563-million.html
Risanamento SpA agreed to sell the
Falck area in Sesto San Giovanni near Milan for 405 million
euros to Sesto Immobiliare SpA, led by Davide Bizzi, according
to a statement distributed by the Italian exchange.  The company said the terma are consistent with its
industrial plan, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
